Package: screenmill
Type: Package
Title: Tools for measuring and annotating arrayed colony data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2022-09-22
Authors@R: c(
    person("Eric", "Bryant", email = "eeb2139@columbia.edu", role = c("aut","cre")),
    person("Robert", "Reid", email = "rr381@cumc.columbia.edu", role = c("aut","edt")))
Maintainer: 'Eric Bryant' <eeb2139@columbia.edu>
Description: This package includes tools for making quantitative measurements of colony growth
    propagated in regular arrays on solid agar plates. It ports most of the functionality of 
    the web version of ScreenMill to an R package. For more information about ScreenMill
    see <http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/20584323>. The R package includes tools for
    analyzing time-series growth data.
